    dc:description "Figure 13. Holotype male of Ichneumon doliturus Smith, 1874 (= Cratichneumon doliturus (Smith,1874)): (a) labels (b) lateral habitus (c) head, frontal view (d) head, dorsal view (e) head, lateral view (f) mesoscutum, dorsal view (g) scutellum and propodeum, dorsal view (h) mesosoma, lateral view (i) wings (j) metasoma, dorsal view." ;
